  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">For others with the same name, see <a href=\"/index.php/Wylla_(disambiguation)\" title=\"Wylla (disambiguation)\">Wylla (disambiguation)</a>.</div>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Fenn\" title=\"House Fenn\"><img alt=\"House Fenn.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/d/d0/House_Fenn.svg/50px-House_Fenn.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/d/d0/House_Fenn.svg/75px-House_Fenn.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/d/d0/House_Fenn.svg/100px-House_Fenn.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Wylla Fenn</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Fenn\" title=\"House Fenn\"><img alt=\"House Fenn.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/d/d0/House_Fenn.svg/50px-House_Fenn.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/d/d0/House_Fenn.svg/75px-House_Fenn.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/d/d0/House_Fenn.svg/100px-House_Fenn.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Wylla_Fenn_Arsa_Stark_and_Alys_Karstark_by_coldraindropsss.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Wylla Fenn Arsa Stark and Alys Karstark by coldraindropsss.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/18/Wylla_Fenn_Arsa_Stark_and_Alys_Karstark_by_coldraindropsss.jpg/300px-Wylla_Fenn_Arsa_Stark_and_Alys_Karstark_by_coldraindropsss.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"296\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/1/18/Wylla_Fenn_Arsa_Stark_and_Alys_Karstark_by_coldraindropsss.jpg/450px-Wylla_Fenn_Arsa_Stark_and_Alys_Karstark_by_coldraindropsss.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/1/18/Wylla_Fenn_Arsa_Stark_and_Alys_Karstark_by_coldraindropsss.jpg/600px-Wylla_Fenn_Arsa_Stark_and_Alys_Karstark_by_coldraindropsss.jpg 2x\" /></a><div>Wylla Fenn, <a href=\"/index.php/Arsa_Stark\" title=\"Arsa Stark\">Arsa Stark</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Alys_Karstark_(wife_of_Brandon)\" title=\"Alys Karstark (wife of Brandon)\">Alys Karstark</a> by coldraindropsss</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Fenn\" title=\"House Fenn\">House Fenn</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Crannogmen\" title=\"Crannogmen\">Crannogmen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Born</th><td>\n~<a href=\"/index.php/100_AC\" title=\"100 AC\">100</a>–<a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_183_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">183&#160;AC</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Calculation_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Calculation-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Died</th><td>\nIn or after <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_152_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">152&#160;AC</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Calculation_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Calculation-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Issue</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Lonnel_Snow\" title=\"Lonnel Snow\">Lonnel Snow</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (appendix)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Wylla Fenn</b> was a noblewoman from <a href=\"/index.php/House_Fenn\" title=\"House Fenn\">House Fenn</a>. She was the mother of Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Brandon_Stark_(son_of_Cregan)\" title=\"Brandon Stark (son of Cregan)\">Brandon Stark</a>'s <a href=\"/index.php/Bastard\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Bastard\">bastard</a> son, <a href=\"/index.php/Lonnel_Snow\" title=\"Lonnel Snow\">Lonnel Snow</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf102.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf102.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Wylla_Fenn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Calculation-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Calculation_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Calculation_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i>See the <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest/Calculations_Ages_(Continued3)#Wylla_Fenn\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest/Calculations Ages (Continued3)\">Wylla Fenn</a> calculation.</i></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiaf102.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf102.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, Appendix&#58; Stark Lineage.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404232331\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.118 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.422 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 478/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node co